{"tid":593424,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"《一人一句經典歌詞/古典文學》往事不回頭，餘生不將就。","createTime":"2018-03-15T03:35:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T04:15:48.000Z","uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2b5de22175457c0415174f5d1856b0a25ee0b714","tid":593424,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:35:27.000Z","msg":"一人一句經典歌詞/古典文學<br />\n<br />\n新歌已經好少聽 可能已經老啦<br />\n以前啲歌真係正到暈 歌詞太中太中心<br />\n以前msn一定會搵句歌詞放status <br />\n有無咩好好聽既舊歌可以分享 尤其係唔太出名<br />\n<br />\n黃偉文 林夕 方文山 李宗盛 係我最鐘意既填詞人<br />\n有時覺得佢地作到呢啲詞  真係受過好重既傷<br />\n我深信佢地內心世界真係好灰<br />\n好似李宗盛因爲性格太怪 情緒太偏<br />\n所以同天後林憶蓮離婚<br />\n有時真係聽到喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  音樂既力量好大<br />\n<br />\n依加聽緊: 失樂園<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oRn1dsLDvUY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DoRn1dsLDvUY&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6fb7a089\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=oRn1dsLDvUY</a><br />\n演唱：草蜢 作曲：周初晨 作詞：黃偉文<br />\n苦戀注定難 我已經習慣 沿途承受不留情的雙眼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5W6BCZvrH_Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D5W6BCZvrH_Q&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=8a67632b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5W6BCZvrH_Q</a><br />\n<br />\n傷心地鐵 作詞：李宗盛　作曲：光良　編曲：Hari Menon/Luke Mason　演唱：光良<br />\n憑一種　啊　男人的直覺　去承受這份殘缺 當緣起和緣滅　我們的過去　已不能重寫<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JGJCFFPzS_c&amp;list=RDJGJCFFPzS_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DJGJCFFPzS_c%26list%3DRDJGJCFFPzS_c&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=55e3485d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JGJCFFPzS_c&amp;list=RDJGJCFFPzS_c</a><br />\n讓 作詞：姚若龍 作曲：蕭煌奇 編曲：Wave G<br />\n我還以為愛 就是要體貼的退讓<br />\n我們一起蓋的羅馬 你卻跟他拆了城牆<br />\n踩過我用摯愛建築的天堂<br />\n太絕對的愛 變成了活該 朋友要我責怪<br />\n我卻只想重來 也許這就叫愛<br />\n多少日子蓋的羅馬 你用一夜拆了城牆<br />\n踩碎我曾讓你棲息的胸膛<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nOULj_5E8EA&amp;t=20s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnOULj_5E8EA%26t%3D20s&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=ef5a06ad\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nOULj_5E8EA&amp;t=20s</a><br />\n離人 土木三年陳同學<br />\n離人放逐到邊界徬佛走入第五個季節 晝夜亂了和諧 漲泛任性漲退 字典里沒春天 離人揮霍著眼淚 回避還在眼前的離別<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------<br />\n90s love songs <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vEplDhmoXMw&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvEplDhmoXMw%26list%3DRDvEplDhmoXMw&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=79f7b66b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vEplDhmoXMw&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LKaXY4IdZ40&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw&amp;index=3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DLKaXY4IdZ40%26list%3DRDvEplDhmoXMw%26index%3D3&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=5591a710\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=LKaXY4IdZ40&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw&amp;index=3</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izGwDsrQ1eQ&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw&amp;index=6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DizGwDsrQ1eQ%26list%3DRDvEplDhmoXMw%26index%3D6&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d193011a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=izGwDsrQ1eQ&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw&amp;index=6</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9AVoIROBt0&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw&amp;index=17\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DY9AVoIROBt0%26list%3DRDvEplDhmoXMw%26index%3D17&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2fc5bccb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Y9AVoIROBt0&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw&amp;index=17</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gnBPHWk5FQ8&amp;index=25&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgnBPHWk5FQ8%26index%3D25%26list%3DRDvEplDhmoXMw&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=cf7aefa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gnBPHWk5FQ8&amp;index=25&amp;list=RDvEplDhmoXMw</a><br />\n<br />\n-------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n文學<br />\n人生若只如初見，何事秋風悲畫扇。<br />\n等閒變卻故人心，卻道故人心易變。<br />\n<br />\n煙花易冷人易散。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n微博文集<br />\n<br />\n往事不回頭，餘生不將就。<br />\n<br />\n妈妈说， 你结婚后流的汗和泪，都是当年选老公时脑子里进的水。<br />\n<br />\n世界這麼大這麼吵 要好好照顧自己 願你餘生不再想起誰<br />\n<br />\n--------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n放住咁多先 有時唔開心聽返歌<br />\n會重拾當初第一次聽既感覺<br />\n當初次聽鍾意左首歌 <br />\n不停重複播嘅一段時光<br />\n真係唔知係分手嘅時候不停聽既個首歌<br />\n再聽已經唔會再喊 但係對嗰一日依然刻骨銘心<br />\n<br />\n 每首歌都代表着一段回憶<br />\n第一次聽嘅時候喺邊度 邊一個同你聽<br />\n好似跑馬燈咁回想返以前<br />\n感嘆就感嘆 傷心嘅傷心 想喊嘅就去喊<br />\n天下起雨了 人是不快樂<br />\n夜晚一個人係屋企着住自己最舒服嘅衫<br />\n睇住風景吹着風聽歌簡直係一個享受<br />\n<br />\n雖然唔係每個人屋企都有好風景<br />\n但點個蠟燭已經好舒服<br />\n<br />\n最後一首歌 晚安。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_4ztL3pt5t8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_4ztL3pt5t8&d=XioFzSu4gs%2FGinipWUyl0ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=6cb8d029\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_4ztL3pt5t8</a><br />\n<br />\n美國時間 23:33<br />\n香港時間 11:33<br />\n澳洲時間 14:33<br />\n英國時間 03:33<br />\n加拿大時間 23:33<br />\n<br />\n給有LD既朋友<br />\n<br />\n願大家身在何處 孤獨的時候 都會有音樂陪伴同連登一班巴絲打既陪伴 <br />\n<br />\nX<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c653350300de45b1da6cd6c2af4b437241f6704","tid":593424,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"Sorry for 1999 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de467d2dde3da4473ac4348aeb0a93126d60e7d6","tid":593424,"uid":175465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T03:55:08.000Z","msg":"原來無人有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a68b0525520a66ccc6a516bbf8e957f3a2c925e","tid":593424,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-15T04:15:48.000Z","msg":"馬個屁股菊花，扒街~"}]}